sequenceDiagram
    actor F as Farmer
    actor B as Buyer
    participant S as AgriGenie System
    participant AI as AI Services
    participant DB as Database
    actor A as Admin

    %% Registration & Approval
    F->>S: Register (phone + PIN)
    B->>S: Register (email + password)
    S->>DB: Create user accounts
    S->>A: Notify new approval requests
    A->>S: Approve / Reject users

    %% Farmer Features
    F->>S: Add crop listing
    S->>DB: Save crop + create marketplace listing

    F->>AI: Upload leaf image
    AI-->>F: Disease name + confidence + treatment

    F->>AI: Request price prediction
    AI-->>F: Predicted prices (7 days)

    F->>AI: Request weather forecast
    AI-->>F: Weather data + disaster alerts

    F->>S: Configure irrigation crops
    S-->>F: Irrigation schedule + water plan

    %% Buyer Flow
    B->>S: Search marketplace
    S-->>B: Matching crop listings

    B->>S: Place order on crop
    S->>DB: Create order (pending)
    S-->>F: Order notification

    F->>S: Accept order
    S-->>B: Order accepted notification

    %% Chat
    B->>S: Start chat with farmer
    S-->>F: Real-time message (WebSocket)
    F->>S: Reply
    S-->>B: Real-time message (WebSocket)

    %% Delivery & Rating
    B->>S: Confirm delivery
    B->>S: Rate farmer + write review
    F->>S: Rate buyer
    S->>DB: Update ratings

    %% Admin Monitoring
    A->>S: View system reports
    S-->>A: User stats, order stats, AI accuracy
